ackward Compatibility**: \u2705 Standard models unchanged\\n\\n### \ud83c\udf1f **Real-World Impact Demonstrated**\\n\\n- **Astronomical Coordinate Transformations**: RA/Dec \u2194 Alt/Az conversions\\n- **Image Processing Pipelines**: Complex transformation chains\\n- **Scientific Modeling**: Physics simulations with custom coupling\\n\\nThe tests prove the bug fix works correctly, enables powerful new capabilities for custom models, and maintains full backward compatibility. All validation tests pass successfully!\\n\\n**Files created:**\\n- `/workspaces/claude-code-flow/astropy_fix/test_serial_composition_fix.py`\\n- `/workspaces/claude-code-flow/astropy_fix/minimal_test_fix.py`\\n- `/workspaces/claude-code-flow/astropy_fix/comprehensive_validation_test.py`\\n- `/workspaces/claude-code-flow/astropy_fix/TEST_VALIDATION_SUMMARY.md`\"}]}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"f1ef38da-70eb-4b82-a5f9-be345c216d40\"}\n{\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_019shiyyqiHKthgJHUyiztTT\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Todos have been modified successfully. Ensure that you continue to use the todo list to track your progress. Please proceed with the current tasks if applicable\"}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"f1ef38da-70eb-4b82-a5f9-be345c216d40\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"id\":\"msg_0167WFFAfVWeaBH6HxihTcmn\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-1-20250805\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now let me synthesize all worker findings and generate the final patch.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":7,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":39020,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"output_tokens\":1,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"f1ef38da-70eb-4b82-a5f9-be345c216d40\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"id\":\"msg_0167WFFAfVWeaBH6HxihTcmn\",\"type\":\"message\"